Reason::NoPerceivedEdge | NoTradeReason::PromptBudgetExceeded, …)` to CAS via `write_market_decision_trace_to_cas` + bumps `tool_dist["invest_no_trade_<label>"]` counter. Closes the trace-or-tx invariant gap: every non-invest market-bearing agent turn now leaves a classifier-bound CAS trace, satisfying SG-G2.6 alongside the existing `"invest"` arm's Submitted / NoTrade dispatch. Predecessor TB-G G2P.1 hash b5c5ec97 superseded.  # rehashed by TB-G G2P.1 (2026-05-12; charter §1 Module G2P atom G2P.1; G-Phase directive §0.6 amendment G-2 "verify_peer=0 比 invest=0 更危险"; closes user 2026-05-12 病灶3 "0 verify"): per-viewer Pending Peer Reviews block wired at the build_agent_prompt site (~line 2188; AFTER econ_position render, BEFORE build_agent_prompt call). Renders queue of accepted peer WorkTxs eligible for this viewer's verify_peer action by calling `turingosv4::sdk::pending_peer_reviews::render_pending_peer_reviews(&q, &AgentId(agent_id.clone()), DEFAULT_PENDING_REVIEWS_K)` against the sequencer's q_snapshot. Empty-string-suppression contract mirrors econ_position. build_agent_prompt signature gains 9th `pending_peer_reviews: &str` arg; the new block lands under canonical "=== Pending Peer Reviews ===" heading in src/sdk/prompt.rs. Pure-read of canonical EconomicState.stakes_t + agent_verifications_t; no private CoT / attempt_telemetry / proposal_cid reads (CLAUDE.md §15 selective shielding). Predecessor TB-N3 A3+A4 hash 36b550c9 superseded.  # rehashed by TB-N3 A3 + A4 hookup (2026-05-11; architect ruling 2026-05-11 amendments 3-6 + Q1+Q2+Q6 + Q7 + amendment 5): (1) full-proof OMEGA WorkTx accept site (post tb8_await_state_root_advance ~line 2772) + per-tactic OMEGA WorkTx accept site (~line 3661) BOTH gain a `TURINGOS_TB_N3_AUTO_MARKET=1`-gated call to `tb_n3_emit_node_market_after_work_accept(&bundle.sequencer, &work_tx_id, &mut reg, "a3-omega-{work_tx_id}", logical_t, seed_micro)` — outcome typed-matched (Created/AlreadyExists/BudgetExhausted/SubmitFailed/PollTimeout) and logged best-effort via info!/warn!. seed_micro reads `TURINGOS_DEFAULT_POOL_SEED_MICRO` env (default 100_000 per architect Q1). (2) Same-task market context A4 wire-up at the build_agent_prompt site (~line 2114): when TB-N3 enabled, derives same-task accepted WorkTx list by walking q.economic_state_t.cpmm_pools_t for event_ids matching `node_survive:` prefix containing the current `task-{run_id}` substring (same-task isolation per amendment 5), then calls `turingosv4::sdk::market_context::render_market_context(&q, &task_id, &same_task_work_tx_ids, K, &agent_id)` with K from `TURINGOS_TB_N3_MARKET_CONTEXT_K` env (default 10 per architect Q7). Result appended to existing TB-14 PriceIndex `market_ticker_str`. Predecessor TB-N3 A2 hash 9942fdf1 superseded.  # rehashed by TB-N3 A2 (2026-05-11; architect ruling 2026-05-11 amendments 1+2 + Q5; charter v3 §3): replaced TB-9-era `invest_disabled_tb9` no-op handler at line 3008 with full TB-N3 A2 invest-routing pipeline. Reads `action.node` (canonical work_tx_id), `action.amount` (microCoin via f64 → i64 cast), `action.direction` ("long"|"yes" → BuyYes; "short"|"no" → BuyNo). When chaintape + agent_keypairs both present: q_snapshot → tb_n3_invest_to_router_tx pre-classify (snapshot mode) → on Ok submit + tb8_await_state_root_advance + write `MarketDecisionTrace::submitted` to CAS via `write_market_decision_trace_to_cas`; on Err map to `NoTradeReason` + write `MarketDecisionTrace::no_trade` to CAS. tool_dist counters: `invest_attempted`, `invest_submitted`, `invest_no_trade_<reason>`, `invest_submit_err`, `invest_snapshot_err`, `invest_no_chaintape`. event_id constructed via `node_survive_event_id` (architect amendment 1: "node market 的 event_id 必须是 accepted WorkTx 的 canonical tx_id，而不是 task_id"). min_out_shares = 0 per architect Q5 MVP. Predecessor TB-N2 B2 R2 hash 31210690 superseded.  # rehashed by TB-N2 B2 R2 race fix (2026-05-11; Codex G2 R1 Q8 VETO closure): both EventResolve emit hooks (full-proof ~line 2823 + p